WEEKI WACHEE ORCHID GARDENS, INC., a Florida corporation, Petitioner, v. FLORIDA INLAND THEATRES, INC., (Successor to St. Petersburg Springs Co.), a Florida corporation, Respondent. No. 40427. Supreme Court of Florida. Feb. 4, 1971. ROBERTS, C. J., and CARLTON, ADKINS, McCAIN and DEKLE, JJ., concur.

Rehearing Denied April 14, 1971.

Certiorari denied. 239 So.2d 602.
